    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游乐园的彩色灯光、笑声与音乐。当你在热狗餐车中为顾客服务时，一切看起来都很平常。但随着夜色加深……人群散去，灯光熄灭，有什么东西开始注视着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Hotdog Butcher》是一款单人恐怖体验游戏。白天你过着普通热狗贩卖者的生活，夜晚则面对黑暗的过去。故事从游乐园开始……接着带你回家、走上街道，甚至深入那些被遗忘的角落。<br><br>准备订单、调好酱料、服务顾客。在彩色灯光下，一切看起来都充满生气……但有些地方不太对劲，而那种感觉一天比一天强烈。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/e8aead7d09d9508e7e79d6468296f829.poster.avif?t=1762385276\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/e8aead7d09d9508e7e79d6468296f829.webm?t=1762385276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/e8aead7d09d9508e7e79d6468296f829.mp4?t=1762385276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与人交谈，每一个回答都会改变故事的方向。有些角色看似友善，有些则在隐藏什么。真相是一个所有人都知道、却没人敢说的秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/c8e68e3f8aa1e214d2535e08f40267a7.poster.avif?t=1762385276\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/c8e68e3f8aa1e214d2535e08f40267a7.webm?t=1762385276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/c8e68e3f8aa1e214d2535e08f40267a7.mp4?t=1762385276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当灯光熄灭时，一切都改变了。探索环境、检查物品，但有时你所看到的，只与你自己有关。每一章都揭示更多的故事，并带来全新的恐惧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/d1616e93a6e6b39bb998c5791e150660.poster.avif?t=1762385276\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/d1616e93a6e6b39bb998c5791e150660.webm?t=1762385276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109560/extras/d1616e93a6e6b39bb998c5791e150660.mp4?t=1762385276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Hotdog Butcher》是一款从平静开始、逐渐变得紧张的单人恐怖体验。故事从一辆热狗餐车开始……而结局，也许会让你开始怀疑，谁才是真正的无辜者。</p>",
